Class AsciiDocDocTreeWalker

java.lang.Object
com.sun.source.util.DocTreeScanner<Void,Void>
com.sun.source.util.DocTreePathScanner<Void,Void>
uk.co.spudsoft.params4j.doclet.AsciiDocDocTreeWalker
All Implemented Interfaces:
DocTreeVisitor<Void,Void>
public class AsciiDocDocTreeWalker extends DocTreePathScanner<Void,Void>
DocTreePathScanner for generating AsciiDocs from JavaDocs HTML content. This is used by the AsciiDocElementVisitor to handle HTML comments.
Author:
njt
